Package: ciphertext
Type: Package
Title: Simple Cryptography Methods for Words and Phrases
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Luigi", "Annicchiarico", email = "luigi.annic@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"))
    )
Description: Simple cryptography methods for words and brief phrases.
    Substitution and transposition methods are available, like
    Caesar, Vigenere, Atbash, affine, simple substitution,
    rail fence, scytale, and single column ciphers.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/Luigi-Annic/ciphertext
BugReports: https://github.com/Luigi-Annic/ciphertext/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.3.0)
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
